<TITLE>
Mhuwe, the Lenape ice giant (Mhwe, Mhwee, Malew)
</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Information and legends about the Native American mythological 
figure Mhuwe (Mhwe), a man-eating ice giant of Lenape folklore.">
